# VAADIN PWA & WEB COMPONENTS

## PWA SETUP
```java
@PWA(name = "MyApp", shortName = "App", iconPath = "icons/logo.png",
     backgroundColor = "#fff", themeColor = "#4285f4", offlinePath = "offline.html")
public class AppShell implements AppShellConfigurator { }
```

## PUSH NOTIFICATIONS (Optional)
```java
WebPushMessage.builder().title("Title").body("Message").icon("/icon.png").build();
```

## WEB COMPONENTS (Optional)
```java
@WebComponentExporter
public class MyExporter extends WebComponentExporter<MyComponent> {
    public MyExporter() { super("my-component"); }
}
```

## REQUIREMENTS
- Icons: 192x192, 512x512
- HTTPS in production (mandatory for PWA)
- Offline page: `src/main/webapp/offline.html`

## ANTIPATTERNS
1. No HTTPS → PWA fails
2. Missing icons → no installation
3. No offline page → blank screen offline
